ygData.messageBody:
As of 6:12 pm Eastern Time we have 116 subscribers to this email list. So
far I have seen nothing but "Great" information on the list and only hope it
gets better. Keep getting the word out, tell your friends or post on
warrior message boards. The more information we get the better. Warriors
are the best class, we just have to work a little harder to keep up with the
others.

I am a level 11 barbarian warrior princess (some might say an Amazon!)
currently hunting in Clan Crushbone on Bristlebane.

I have added the links found in warriors_eq email to onelist.com. You can
view or add your own links by going to www.onelist.com, signing in, and
clicking on the warriors_eq list. Here you will find a bunch of options,
one of them being "bookmarks."

By the way, I plan to us two combine long swords when I get to level 15.
Not because I know any better, but because it looks so cool.

For the Honor and Glory of Rallos Zek;

Patty of Halas
username: Patricia
server: Bristlebane
